# {{ ip }} session status sidecars

Generated by uvm-gen {{ gen_version }}. This directory holds the
machine-readable verdicts the Copilot DV pack drops here; the local cockpit
(`verif-cockpit` skill) renders pending human decisions and the scorecard
from them. Kept tracked (this README) so the directory exists from day one.

Files that land here:

| File | Written by | Contents |
|---|---|---|
| `session_<date>.json` | every agent session | `{agent, gate, status, open_questions[], handoffs[], rtl_rev}` (evidence contract) |
| `review.json` | `verif-env-review` | 9-axis scorecard, milestone verdict, `dod_pass` |
| `lint.json` | `deprecation-lint` (`lint.py`) | independence/deprecation findings |
| `triage.json` | `regression-triage` | clustered failure signatures |

Regenerate the cockpit after a batch of runs:

```bash
python3 .github/skills/verif-cockpit/scripts/cockpit.py {{ ip }} --config template/cockpit.ini
```

(These JSON files are runtime artifacts — git-ignore them per your team policy
if you prefer; the schema above is the contract the cockpit reads.)
